videos.headline: Air Force scores first on a QB keeper
videos.description: Haaziq Daniels calls his own number for a 5-yard touchdown to get Air Force on the board first.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Air Force strikes first on a QB keeper) 2021/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Air Force doubles lead on 61-yard TD pass
videos.description: Air Force goes up 14-0 over Louisville as Haaziq Daniels finds Brandon Lewis for the 61-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Air Force doubles lead on 61-yard TD pass) 2021/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Air Force WR sends two Louisville defenders to the ground with ridiculous cutbacks
videos.description: Brandon Lewis had the Louisville defenders on skates as he takes it in for the 64-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Air Force WR sends two Louisville defenders to the ground with ridiculous cutbacks) 2021/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jawhar Jordan takes the kickoff 100 yards for the TD
videos.description: Louisville makes it a one-possession game versus Air Force after Jawhar Jordan takes the kickoff for a 100-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jawhar Jordan takes the kickoff 100 yards for the TD) 2021/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haaziq Daniels scores second TD on the day
videos.description: Haaziq Daniels doubles Air Force's lead as they go up 28-14 over Louisville with less than a minute to go in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Haaziq Daniels scores second TD on the day) 2021/12/28 ESHEET
